      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is a commercially validated solver with documented QA processes. All case files, UDFs, and post-processing scripts are stored in a Git repository (tag v3.2.1) with SHA-256 checksums verified at runtime. No custom solver modifications were introduced."
