    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are explicitly not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Validation evidence demonstrates RH predictions within 9.4% of experimental measurements across all operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Mesh convergence is confirmed with GCI < 2.5% on the fine mesh. The credibility evidence package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
